1. Unzip, untar and upload everything to your webdirectory.

2. Set folder and file permissions to

cache	777/666
config	755/644
doc		755/644
objects	755/644
source	755/644
sql		755/644
xslt	755/644
upload	777/666

3a. run /path/to/your/webdir/install.php and follow instructions
for databse setup and system configuration

or

3b. edit /config/config.inc.php manually and execute database scripts
from /sql

4. finished